Version:        3.20.2
Release:        0
Summary:        Cross-platform make system
License:        BSD-3-Clause
URL:            https://www.cmake.org/
Source0:        https://www.cmake.org/files/v%{shortversion}/cmake-%{version}.tar.gz
Source1:        cmake.macros
